
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device"><title>web design and administration on html on multi-iframes on a webpage</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .controls {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4a6ee0;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #3a5eca;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .iframe-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .iframe-wrapper {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .iframe-wrapper:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .iframe-header {
            padding: 15px 20px;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .iframe-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
        }

        .iframe-actions button {
            padding: 5px 10px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            background-color: #64748b;
        }

        iframe {
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
            border: none;
            display: block;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .iframe-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
